---
layout: page.njk
title: Amherst Community Band
description: The homepage of the Amherst Community Band from Amherst, Massachusetts.
---
{% set firstConcert = config.concerts[0].schedule_items[0] %}
{% set firstRehearsal = config.rehearsals[0].schedule_items[0] %}

<section class="section pt-3 pb-3">
    <div class="home-hero carousel" data-flickity='{"setGallerySize":true,"wrapAround":true,"autoPlay":6500,"pauseAutoPlayOnHover":true}'>
        {% for slide in config.carouselImages %}
            <div class="carousel-cell home-hero-slide">
                <div class="home-hero-image-wrap">
                    {% image "src" + slide.imgPath, slide.altText, "(min-width: 1024px) 960px, (min-width: 768px) 80vw, 100vw" %}
                    <p class="home-hero-caption is-size-4 has-text-weight-semibold">{{ slide.caption|safe }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section pt-0 pb-4">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content has-text-centered home-season-announcement mx-auto" style="max-width: 50rem;">
            <h2 class="title is-3 mb-4">Rehearsals begin Monday, June 8, 2026!</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
                Our Summer season is right around the corner. We&rsquo;re planning an exciting lineup of music and guest conductors. If you play an instrument, please consider joining us. All are welcome!
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
                <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BAiRqI2M5HVDRtvIcswyIRhhGg_DB7npbs3DAl_eka8/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    Here&rsquo;s the schedule for the full season.
                </a>
            </p>
            <p class="has-text-weight-semibold mb-3">We are grateful to our scheduled guest conductors!</p>
            <p class="mb-3"><strong>June 27 &amp; July 3 Concerts</strong><br>Dave Morris, Conductor<br>Alexandria (Lexie) Black, Assistant Conductor</p>
            <p class="mb-3"><strong>July 25 Concert</strong><br>Juli Sansoucy, Conductor</p>
            <p class="mb-0"><strong>August 15 &amp; 18 Concerts</strong><br>Richard Cuoco, Conductor</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section pt-2">
    <div class="home-welcome has-soft-corners p-5 has-background-info-light">
        <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered mb-3">Welcome to the Amherst Community Band</h1>
        <p class="is-size-5 has-text-centered mb-4">
            The Amherst Community Band is made up of high school students, college students, and adults, some of whom are in their 80's.
        </p>
        <p class="has-text-centered mb-0">
            Whether you play right now or have not played in years, you will feel right at home. Best of all, we are audition-free.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section pt-3 pb-3">
    <div class="columns is-variable is-4">
        <div class="column is-half-desktop is-half-tablet is-full-mobile is-flex">
            <article class="home-info-card has-soft-corners p-5">
                <h2 class="title is-4">Next Concert</h2>
                <p class="is-size-6 has-text-weight-semibold mb-2">{{ firstConcert.date_and_time }}</p>
                {% if firstConcert.concert_name %}
                    <p class="mb-2">{{ firstConcert.concert_name }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                <p class="mb-4">{{ firstConcert.location }}</p>
                <a class="button is-primary has-text-weight-bold has-text-white" href="{{ '/performances/' | withBase }}">View All Performances</a>
            </article>
        </div>

        <div class="column is-half-desktop is-half-tablet is-full-mobile is-flex">
            <article class="home-info-card has-soft-corners p-5">
                <h2 class="title is-4">Rehearsal Information</h2>
                <p class="is-size-6 has-text-weight-semibold mb-2">{{ config.rehearsals[0].label }}</p>
                <p class="mb-4">{{ firstRehearsal.date_and_time }}</p>
                <a class="button is-primary has-text-weight-bold has-text-white" href="{{ '/members/' | withBase }}">For Members</a>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section pt-3">
    <div class="columns is-multiline is-variable is-4">
        <div class="column is-half-desktop is-half-tablet is-full-mobile is-flex">
            <article class="home-action-card has-soft-corners p-5">
                <h2 class="title is-4">Join Us</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">If you play an instrument, please consider joining us. All are welcome.</p>
                <a class="button is-primary has-text-weight-bold has-text-white" href="{{ '/join/' | withBase }}">Learn About Joining</a>
            </article>
        </div>

        <div class="column is-half-desktop is-half-tablet is-full-mobile is-flex">
            <article class="home-action-card has-soft-corners p-5">
                <h2 class="title is-4">Performances</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">Our concerts are free and open to the public throughout the summer, plus a winter concert each year.</p>
                <a class="button is-primary has-text-weight-bold has-text-white" href="{{ '/performances/' | withBase }}">See the Schedule</a>
            </article>
        </div>

        <div class="column is-half-desktop is-half-tablet is-full-mobile is-flex">
            <article class="home-action-card has-soft-corners p-5">
                <h2 class="title is-4">For Members</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">Check rehearsal details, member information, and updates for current players.</p>
                <a class="button is-primary has-text-weight-bold has-text-white" href="{{ '/members/' | withBase }}">Go to Members Page</a>
            </article>
        </div>

        <div class="column is-half-desktop is-half-tablet is-full-mobile is-flex">
            <article class="home-action-card has-soft-corners p-5">
                <h2 class="title is-4">Donate</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">Help us buy music, rent trucks, and make music in our community with your generous online contributions.</p>
                <a class="button is-primary has-text-weight-bold has-text-white" href="{{ '/donate/' | withBase }}">Support the Band</a>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section pt-1">
    <div class="columns is-centered is-8">
        <div class="column is-3">
            <a href="http://www.massculturalcouncil.org/">
                {% image "src/_images/MCC_Logo_RGB_NoTag.png", "Mass Cultural Council Logo", "(max-height: auto)" %}
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-3">
            {% image "src/_images/amherst_cultural_council.jpg", "Amherst Cultural Council Logo", "(max-height: auto)" %}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container has-text-centered">
        <h2 class="title is-4">This program is funded in part by a grant from the Amherst Cultural Council, a local agency which is supported by Mass Cultural Council, a state agency.</h2>
    </div>
</section>
